        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Are these tools better than hiring an SEO content writer?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">For volume and consistency, yes. A freelance SEO writer produces 4–8 articles per month. theStacc publishes 30. The per-article cost is $3.30 versus $150–$300. The trade-off: a skilled writer produces nuanced, expert-level content on complex topics. For most business blogs targeting informational keywords, automated tools deliver sufficient quality at 10x the volume.</div>
